description: We are a unique "Food Truck" service dishing up the finest, most delicious pierogi in Central, Ohio. We are family owned & operated with a strong legacy in fine dinning and catering services. We are proud to say that we have been satisfying the hungry masses with our classy look and great taste for nearly two decades. We can create a memorable dinning experience whether we are the culinary main event or a complimentary addition to your existing menu - that nice suprise your guests won't soon forget!In addition to serving the best Pierogi in Central, Ohio, we also provide Catering, Food Truck Service, Fine Dinning Parties, and more. Our vast experience and unique style will create the perfect menu for your Birthday, Anniversary, Reunion, Wedding, Graduation, office picnic, and so much more.
name: Sophie's Gourmet Foods
